        <div id="box4" class="boxcustom">
            <img src="~/img/store/4.png" alt="popsicles">

            <h2 id="popsicles" class="subheading">Ice-cream popsicle</h2>

            <h3>400Tk</h3>
            <p>
                Have faith in Ice-cream is anything with popsicle!<br>
                So enjoy some Ice-cream popsicle.
            </p>

            <div class="button_cont" align="center">
                <a class="example_c" onclick="productP4()" href="../Home/ProductDetails" target="_blank"
                   rel="nofollow noopener">Order Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="box5" class="boxcustom">
            <img src="~/img/store/5.png" alt="cupcakes">

            <h2 id="cupcakes" class="subheading">Colourful Cupcakes</h2>

