                A cupcake a day keeps the tummy rumbles away, so order now from Bakehouse.
            </p>
            <div class="button_cont" align="center">
                <a class="example_c" onclick="productP5()" href="../Home/ProductDetails" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Order Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="box6" class="boxcustom">
            <img src="~/img/store/6.png" alt="swiss-roll">

            <h2 id="swiss-roll" class="subheading">Swiss Roll Dessert</h2>

            <h3>400Tk</h3>
            <p>
                Nothing tastes better than a Swiss Roll Dessert with insane taste of flavors, which is always available
                at our Bakehouse.
            </p>

            <div class="button_cont" align="center">
                <a class="example_c" onclick="productP6()" href="../Home/ProductDetails" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Order Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>

<script>
    function myFunction() {
        var x = document.getElementById("myTopnav");
        if (x.className === "topnav") {
            x.className += " responsive";
        } else {
            x.className = "topnav";
        }
    }
</script>

